<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2015-07-10</DATELINE><TITLE>Biology and Diseases of Swine</TITLE><BODY>Swine are used in biomedical research as models for biomedical research and for teaching. This chapter covers normative biology and behavior along with common and emerging swine diseases. Xenotransplantation is discussed along with similarities and differences of swine immunology.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>